{
  "text": "CTAs. Results of the Sp17 T cell responses reported here were compared to those obtained for the PASD1 antigen in two previous studies using cells from the same cohort of DLBCL patients [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Cells from ten patients were able to mount CTL responses to both Sp17 and PASD1 CTAs (Supplementary Table 2 ). CD4 Th responses to both the PASD1 and Sp17 antigens were also detected in five of these patients.",
  "correct_citation": {
